More to come in v3.
Dfs operate 90%, still needs to add a void in player.java
Major bugs fixed.
Enriched Evo. EXPANSION PACK. Version 2
[img]http://r9.fodey.com/2029/7d90347fb6ce4e64b53c66f37a2a645c.0.gif[/img]
[size=15pt] Thanks to :) :D : Moparscapians and their utterly good remarks, Zlyricale, Palidino76, Cachard, Max, The Reaper X, The Soul. i just love them. THE SOUL AND THE REAPER X teh ownage much??? Arlen [/size]
Features in Expansion Version 1 =
[size=15pt]RETRIBUTION WORKING! Though, i can't fixed the part where to tell the engine to create gfx before the player died. But it works like normal! (maxhit 14). Oh and all godwars npc now talk at a random given time. They drop too.[/size] * ::mkn ( A full inventory of food.)
* ::maxyt (Hp instantly 99.) * ::gomaxx ( Unlimited Spec)
*full prayer draining etc. * ::demote name
* Summoning base. (New)
* Simple Thieving Class (New)
* Simple Fishing base (New)
* Simple Mining base (New)
* ::tendang (kick) (New)
* ::givecommando (Giveadmin in russia) (New)
* ::givepangkat (givemod)
* ::armour
* ::melee
* ::cachardoutfit
* ::void
* ::buatgrafik (gfx id)
* ::interfaceo (interface i.e interface 1000, disconnects you.)
* ::buatnpc (spawnsnpc)
* ::armpk (basic pk stuff) (New)
* ::range
* Fixed, Npc following and updated the npc class. (New)
* ::adminhq (admin relaxing spot) (New)
* ::runes (runes)
* A few added weapon speacial attacks.
* Player Following (Player follows the enemy player if the enemy runs away when in a duel or in a fight) (New)
* Basic burying.
* Fletching System (Revised) (New)
* Class for handling Retribution (Retribution works. Inflicts randomly (up to 14 damage) on players within a range of 3 squares when died)
* Edgeville is 1v1. ( Command is ::edge. If multi is requested, one shall need to go to ::wildy)
* Stable, and can go on even if being attacked. (a.k.a unsyi-able)
* Doesn't use hell too much memory unlike blakescape base.
* ::kq (kalphite queen) (drops things)
* ::kbd (king black dragon) You may also go there via glory operate. Just wear an amulet of glory, and operate it. (New)
* Piety works. Actually has effect on your hit. Multiplied by 0.270
* Prayer works.
* Simple fightcaves minigame. (New) (Type ::fightcaves and you shall be teleported to the entrance to fightcaves)
* Updated Jad Attacks. (New) (Jad starts throwing projectiles(Magic, and Ranged) if you are within 8 steps.)
* Player Defence bonus and maxhit (Updated to meet the demands of players who wants it to be realistic).
* Simple but 'smexy' clan wars minigame. (New)
* Basic Clan Chat. Type '/' to talk in clan. Clan prefix is set to EnrichedEvo.
* Abyssal Demons. ::abbydemons (New(Basic random timer, that sometimes it will teleport at a fixed location around and near you)
* Range specs. Dragon bow projectiles, rune cbow projectiles, karil's crossbow projectiles. Magic shortbow special
* Basic magic defence. (Your magic defence bonus does have an effect on a mager that casts Ice Barrage upon you.)
* Ice barrage Autocast System.
* ::bunuh (Instantly kills a player that you choose and sends them a warning. Usage : ::bunuh name.
* ::matiko (Inflicts 30 damage on a player that you have chosen and sending them a message/ Forced chat. Usage : Same as above.)
